entries.s_20: Ah, Corellian ale. There's nothing better. I've never had a Naboo ale that even comes close.
entries.s_21: Some Gungans called the Muskeg were asking about Hunnos?
entries.s_22: Yes, that's right. What of it? Look, I just got some Corellian ale. Would you mind letting me drink in peace?
entries.s_43: What a view. I love it here. I need a drink.
entries.s_56: Ah, Corellian ale. How wonderful. What brought this on?
entries.s_58: Oh, nothing. Just wanted to talk.
entries.s_59: Oh, great. More people wanting to talk. Just like those Gungans that came by not long ago. The Muskeg, I think they called themselves. Came by asking about my son Hunnos just before he escaped. My lousy, good for nothing son, I mean. Escapes from the RSF and doesn't even bother to come see his father.
